  "story": {
    "title": "The Wise Choice in Bad Weather",
    "body": "One day in a small community, the weather suddenly became very bad. Dark clouds covered the sky, and strong wind started blowing. Rafi and his pet were walking home from school when they faced a difficult situation. The distance to home was long, and they had to make a choice quickly. Rafi remembered his teacher’s instruction to always stay calm and think wisely. He avoided dangerous areas and chose a safe road instead. On the way, he saw a frightened man who had fallen and could not reach his house. Rafi helped him, even though it made their return slower. Later, a loud storm spread across the village, but they survived safely. The man thanked Rafi with a kind voice and said he was very wise. Rafi felt upset about the storm but content that he made the right decision. That day he learned that a wise choice can save lives and help others too.",
